
Events : 
-------
Every action which can change the state of an object is known as event.

(object)
Button --------> click (action) ------> Action performed
                     |
                   Event 
                     |-- Event handler 
                     |-- Event handler function 

    <button onclick="myFun()">Click Me</button>
               |       |
     Event Handler     |
               Event Handler Function   
       

Types of Events : 
    a. Mouse Event 
        |-- onmouseover 
        |-- onmousemove
        |-- onmouseenter 
        |-- onmouseleave
        |-- onmousedown 
        |-- onmouseup
        |-- onmousewheel 
        |-- click event 
                |-- onclick
                |-- ondblclick (dbl for double click)
                |-- oncontextmenu (for right click)

    b. Key Events   
        |-- onkeyup
        |-- onkeydown 
        |-- onkeypress 

    c. Form Event 
        |-- onsubmit 
        |-- onchange
        |-- onfocus 
        |-- onblur 

    d. Window Event | Load Event 
        |-- onload 
        |-- onunload 

In case of Html
  img, input, button <------ element 
  <img height="" width="" src="">
     here height, width and src are attributes         

In case of JavaScript
  img, input, button <------ object 
  <img height="" width="" src="">
     here height, width and src are properties         


